author: Mitch Stephens
title: McClymonds-Oakland: Still among the Bay Area’s best
text: When 15 starters, including Chronicle Metro Player of the Year LaVance Warren , graduated from last year’s unbeaten (on the field) team, McClymonds-Oakland football coach Michael Peters had few expectations heading into 2015.
